This is a '''list of awards named after Governors General of Canada'''. It has become a tradition for [[Governor General of Canada|governors general]] to establish a trophy, grant, scholarship, or other award in sport, the arts, academia, or professional fields, either during their tenure or just prior to their departure from the office. [[Viceregal consort of Canada|Viceregal consorts]] may also create awards, such as the [[Lady Byng Memorial Trophy]], named for [[Evelyn Byng, Viscountess Byng of Vimy]]; these, however, are not included in this list.
